{
  "stem": "1415.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] After-- after that ghetto, my brother found out-- my brother Herschel, who was my oldest brother-- he was 13 years older than me-- he found out about that they're going to have a selection.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he had planned this a long time already while we were still in our own home, which I found out later.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They-- they build a bunker under a chicken farm in that open ghetto, and the whole family was put in there.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He was a-- a Jewish policeman.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He was 20 years old.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he put us all-- he-- into that-- into that bunker under the chicken coop, the whole family, whoever he could get to go under there.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we waited out the first selection.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] By the time-- also, I-- I forgot again.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "During the open ghetto time, there were a lot of hangings.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they were all done in that marketplace, which was right in front of our buildings all over.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they used-- it started out with the-- the heads of-- of Ostrowiec, which most of them were not even Jews.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It started out with the hangings, and we all were invited to watch.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We had to watch, in other words.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And also, a very important thing happened during that time is that my brother Jonathan, who is the second oldest, he ran away during the beginning-- very beginning of the war.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "He ran away to Litva.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And in-- in doing so, he found out that they were-- Jews were being unkindly treated.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "He went to the Red Cross over in Litva, and he demanded to know how we are.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So I recall when-- when the SS came into our house, and they took us all.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
